{"title_page": "Pragya Yadav", "text_new": "\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2018}}\n{{Infobox fashion designer\n| name               = Pragya Kapoor\n| image              = Abhishek Kapoor and Pragya Yadav at Abu Jani-Sandeep Khosla show for \u2018Volvo S90\u2019.jpg\n| caption            = Pragya Kapoor with her husband\n Abhishek Kapoor\n| nationality        = Indian\n| occupation         = Actress, producer, environmentalist\n| birth_name         = \n| birth_date         = {{birth-date and age|29 June 1990}}\n| birth_place        = [[Borgholm, Sweden]]\n| death_date         = \n| death_place        = \n| education          = \n| spouse             = Abhishek Kapoor\n| label_name         = \n| significant_design = \n| awards             = \n| website            = \n}}\n\n'''Praga Yadav''', also known as '''Pragya Kapoor''', is a Swedish-Indian model, actress, and producer. {{r|ref5}}She was born in [[Borgholm]] and raised in [[Karlskrona]], Sweden. She has trained in acting at the Institute of Advanced Acting and Behavioral Studies. {{r|ref7}}\n\nShe married film director and producer [[Abhishek Kapoor]] on 4 May 2015. {{r|ref4}}They have two children, Isana and Shamsher. {{r|ref1}}\n\n== Career ==\nPragya Kapoor is best known for her work in [[Amole Gupte]]'s ''[[Hawaa Hawaai]] (2014).'' {{r|ref6}}She has produced ''[[Kedarnath (film)|Kedarnath]] (2018)'' with [[Ronnie Screwvala]], along with Abhishek Kapoor and Abhishek Nayyar as co-producers. {{r|ref8}}She is the co-founder of Guy In The Sky Pictures. {{r|ref9}}In collaboration with [[Bhushan Kumar]]'s T Series, she was to be producing ''Sharaabi''. {{r|ref11}}\n\n==Filmography==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+Key\n| style=\"background:#ffc;\"| {{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n| Denotes films that have not yet been released\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-  style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n!scope=\"col\"| Year\n!scope=\"col\"| Title\n!scope=\"col\"| Role\n!scope=\"col\"| Notes\n|-\n|2014\n\n!scope=\"row\"| ''[[Hawaa Hawaai]]''\n| Pragya Nanda\n|\n|}\n\n== Social work and activism ==\nPragya Kapoor is an [[environmentalist]], she has participated actively in cleanliness drives and beach clean-ups to save the environment. {{r|ref2}}She organized a beach clean-up with the Mahim beach cleanup team to raise awareness about [[plastic pollution]]. {{r|ref3}}On her son Isana's birthday she hosted a [[Zero waste|zero-waste]] party. {{r|ref10}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|refs=\n\n<ref name=ref1>[https://www.bollywoodshaadis.com/articles/abhishek-kapoor-shares-a-beautiful-chill-session-of-pragya-kapoor-and-son-11271]{{dead link|date=January 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=ref2>{{cite web|url=https://www.mid-day.com/articles/pragya-kapoor-has-some-special-plans-for-son-shamshers-first-birthday/21625153 |title=Pragya Kapoor has some special plans for son Shamsher's first birthday - entertainment |publisher=Mid-day.com |date=2019-08-28 |accessdate=2020-01-16}}</ref>\n<ref name=ref3>{{cite web|url=https://www.mid-day.com/articles/pragya-kapoor-celebrates-her-son-shamshers-first-birthday-with-a-conscious-initiative/21656156 |title=Pragya Kapoor celebrates her son Shamsher's first birthday with a conscious initiative - entertainment |publisher=Mid-day.com |date=2019-09-01 |accessdate=2020-01-16}}</ref>\n<ref name=ref4>[https://www.bollywoodshaadis.com/articles/abhishek-kapoor-and-pragya-yadav-embrace-parenthood-again-9700]{{dead link|date=January 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=ref5>{{cite web|url=https://www.samacharlive.com/sara-ali-khans-graph-was-amazing-to-watch-says-pragya-kapoor/ |title=Sara Ali Khan\u2019s graph was Amazing to Watch Says Pragya Kapoor |publisher=Samachar Live |date=2018-12-21 |accessdate=2020-01-16}}</ref>\n<ref name=ref6>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Pragya-Yadav-Amole-Gupte-Abhishek-Kapoor-Kai-Po-Che/articleshow/23161777.cms |title=pragya yadav: How Pragya Yadav ba