it University F.C.|Rangsit University]]\n|-\n|align=center rowspan=\"2\"|3\n|{{flag|Phra Nakhon Si Ayutthaya}}||align=center|2||align=center|[[Bankunmae F.C.|Bankunmae]] and [[Pathumthani University F.C.|Pathumthani University]]\n|-\n|{{flag|Nonthaburi}}||align=center|2||align=center|[[Muangthong United F.C.|SCG Muangthong United (B)]] and [[Siam F.C.|Siam]]\n|-\n|align=center|5\n|{{flag|Samut Prakan}}||align=center|1||align=center|[[Samut Prakan F.C.|Samut Prakan]]\n|}\n{{clear}}\n\n=== Stadiums and locations ===\n{{location map+ |Thailand |width=380 |float=right |caption=Locations of the 2019 Thai League 4 Bangkok Metropolitan region teams |places=\n{{Location map~ |Thailand |lat=13.766570 |long=100.552823|label_size=80|label={{Background color|#ffffdd|{{nowrap|'''Bangkok Metro'''}}}}|mark=black pog.svg|marksize=11  |position=bottom}}\n{{location map~ |Thailand |lat=14.333084 |long=100.404973|label_size=80|label={{Background color|#ffffdd|[[Bankunmae F.C.|Bankunmae]]}}|position=top}}\n{{location map~ |Thailand |lat=14.169186 |long=100.529242|label_size=80|label={{Background color|#ffffdd|[[Pathumthani University F.C.|Pathumthani University]]}}|position=right}}\n\n<!--DISPLAY OF BANGKOK TEAMS IN BOTTOM RIGHT CORNER-->\n{{Location map~ |Thailand |mark=TransparentPlaceholder.png |marksize=2  |lat=11.328136|long=100.312389|label_size=80|label='''Bangkok&nbsp;Metro&nbsp;teams'''<br />\n<div style=label_size=80>\n{{nowrap|[[Air Force Robinson F.C.|Air Force Robinson]]<br />\n [[Air Force United F.C.|Air Force United (B)]]<br />\n [[Bangkok United F.C.|Bangkok United (B)]]<br />\n [[Grakcu Sai Mai United F.C.|Grakcu Sai Mai United]]<br />\n [[Police Tero F.C.|Police Tero (B)]]<br />\n [[Rangsit United F.C.|Rangsit United]]<br />\n [[Rangsit University F.C.|Rangsit University]]<br />\n [[Samut Prakan F.C.|Samut Prakan]]<br />\n [[Muangthong United F.C.|SCG Muangthong United (B)]]<br />\n [[Siam F.C.|Siam]]<br />\n [[Thonburi University F.C.|Thonburi University]]}}\n</div>