o F.C.|Police Tero (B)]]\n|name_RTD=[[Rangsit United F.C.|Rangsit United]]\n|name_RSU=[[Rangsit University F.C.|Rangsit University]]\n|name_SPK=[[Samut Prakan F.C.|Samut Prakan]]\n|name_SMU=[[Muangthong United F.C.|SCG Muangthong United (B)]]\n|name_SAM=[[Siam F.C.|Siam]]\n|name_TBU=[[Thonburi University F.C.|Thonburi University]]\n\n<!--Table settings and rules-->\n|show_limit=5\n|class_rules=1) Points; 2) Head-to-head points; 3) Head-to-head goal difference; 4) Head-to-head goal scored; 5) Overall goal difference; 6) Overall goal scored; 7) Fair play points; 8) Play-off without extra time).\n\n<!--Qualification and relegation column definitions-->\n|res_col_header=QR\n|col_T4CL=#ACE1AF |text_T4CL={{nowrap|Qualification to the [[2019 Thai League 4 #Champions League stage|Champions League stage]]}}\n|col_REL=red1 |text_REL=Relegation to the [[Thailand Amateur League|2020 Thailand Amateur League]]\n|col_SUS=red2 |text_SUS=Suspension in 2020 season\n\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n===Positions by round===\n{{#invoke:Sports rbr table|table\n| title = \n| sortable = y\n| team10 = [[Air Force Robinson F.C.|Air Force Robinson]]\n| pos10  = 8/13/12/10/8/9/9/9/10/9/11/10/9/10/9/9/9/10/9/9/10/10/10/10/10/10\n| team13 = [[Air Force United F.C.|Air Force United (B)]]\n| pos13  = 1*/5/10/11/11/12/13*/12/9/10/13*/13*/13*/13*/13*/13*/13*/13*/13*/13*/13*/13*/13*/13*/13*/13*\n| team2 = [[Bangkok United F.C.|Bangkok United (B)]]\n| pos2  = 7/6/4/3/3/4/3/3/2*/1*/1*/2*/1*/1*/3/2*/3/3/3/3/3/3/2*/2*/2*/2*\n| team8 = [[Bankunmae F.C.|Bankunmae]]\n| pos8  = 10/10/7/4/4/2/4/6/5/5/5/6/7/7/7/7/7/7/7/7/7/8/8/8/8/8\n| team6 = [[Grakcu Sai Mai United F.C.|Grakcu Sai Mai United]]\n| pos6  = 11/9/8/6/6/6/6/5/7/6/6/5/4/4/5/5/4/5/5/4/4/4/5/6/6/6\n| team3 = [[Pathumthani University F.C.|Pathumthani University]]\n| pos3  = 3/2/3/5/5/5/5/2/4/4/2/3/3/3/2/3/2/2/2/2/2/2/3/3/3/3\n| team5 = [[Police Tero F.C.|Police Tero (B)]]\n| pos5  = 2*/1*/1*/1*/2*/3/2*/4/3/3/4/4/5/5/4/4/5/4/4/6/6/5/4/4/5/5\n| team11 = [[Rangsit