ract\n| 10 December 2012\n| Pre-Season\n| {{flagicon|BLR}} [[Oleg Kubarev]]\n| 7 February 2013\n|-\n| [[Il\u016bkstes NSS|Il\u016bkste]]\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Alens Vinakurovs]]\n| Own  decision\n| 6 March 2013\n| Pre-Season\n| {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Vladimir Pachko]]\n| 6 March 2013\n|-\n| [[FK Jelgava|Jelgava]]\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[J\u0101nis Dreimanis]]\n| Health issues\n| 22 March 2013\n| Pre-Season\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Sergejs Golubevs]]\n| 22 March 2013\n|-\n| [[FK Spartaks J\u016brmala|Spartaks]]\n| {{flagicon|BLR}} [[Oleg Kubarev]]\n| Sacked\n| 27 July 2013\n| 5th\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Aleksandrs Stradi\u0146\u0161]]\n| 27 July 2013\n|-\n| [[FK Spartaks J\u016brmala|Spartaks]]\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Aleksandrs Stradi\u0146\u0161]]\n| Sacked\n| 22 September 2013\n| 6th\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Jurijs Popkovs]]\n| 22 September 2013\n|-\n| [[Il\u016bkstes NSS|Il\u016bkste]]\n| {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Vladimir Pachko]]\n| Own  decision\n| End of September\n| 10th\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Alens Vinakurovs]]\n| End of September\n|}\n\n== Broadcasting ==\nAs in the previous season most of the matches are being transmitted live via ''sportacentrs.com'' online and sportacentrs TV channel.<ref name=\"sportacentrs\">{{cite web|url=http://sportacentrs.com/sportacentrs_tv/|title=sportacentrs.com|publisher=sportacentrs.com|accessdate=December 1, 2015}}</ref> In June 2012 broadcasting rights were also bought by the English company [[Bet365]].<ref name=\"kasjauns\">{{cite web|url=http://www.kasjauns.lv/lv/zinas/83562/pirmo-reizi-vesture-pardotas-latvijas-virsligas-futbola-cempionata-interneta-translaciju-tiesibas|title=Pirmo reizi v\u0113stur\u0113 p\u0101rdotas Latvijas virsl\u012bgas futbola \u010dempion\u0101ta interneta transl\u0101ciju ties\u012bbas &#124; Kasjauns.lv|publisher=kasjauns.lv|accessdate=December 1, 2015}}</ref> Since 2012, the league's homepage ''futbolavirsliga.lv'' has been active and since September 2012 this website has been accompanied by the InStat Football system, showing information and analysis of each match individually.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://futbolavirsliga.lv/index.php/jaunumi/780-virsliga-plano-ieviest-kvalitativu-statistikas-un-analizes-sistemu |title=Archived copy |access-date=2013-03-25 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130219030923/http://futbolavirsliga.lv/index.php/jaunumi/780-virsliga-plano-ieviest-kvalitativu-statistikas-un-analizes-sistemu |archive-date=2013-02-19 |url-status=dead }}</ref> Since October 2012, the Virsl\u012bga has also had its own analytical broadcast after each round of matches with football experts discussing the games and future events connected to Latvian football. It is transmitted via sportacentrs TV.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://futbolavirsliga.lv/index.php/jaunumi/1061-virsligai-savs-apskata-raidijums |title=Archived copy |access-date=2013-03-25 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130218233647/http://futbolavirsliga.lv/index.php/jaunumi/1061-virsligai-savs-apskata-raidijums |archive-date=2013-02-18 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n== League table ==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n\n|team1=VEN|name_VEN=[[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]]\n|team2=SKO|name_SKO=[[Skonto FC|Skonto]]\n|team3=DGD|name_DGD=[[FC Daugava|Daugava Daugavpils]]\n|team4=DGR|name_DGR=[[FK Daugava (2003)|Daugava R\u012bga]]\n|team5=LIE|name_LIE=[[FK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs|Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs]]\n|team6=FCJ|name_FCJ=[[FC J\u016brmala|J\u016brmala]]\n|team7=SPJ|name_SPJ=[[FK Spartaks J\u016brmala|Spartaks J\u016brmala]]\n|team8=JEL|name_JEL=[[FK Jelgava|Jelgava]]\n|team9=MLU|name_MLU=[[FS METTA/Latvijas Universit\u0101te|METTA/LU]]\n|team10=ILU|name_ILU=[[Il\u016bkstes NSS]]\n|win_VEN=21|draw_VEN=4|loss_VEN=2|gf_VEN=65|ga_VEN=19|status_VEN=C\n|win_SKO=18|draw_SKO=8|loss_SKO=1|gf_SKO=68|ga_SKO=11\n|win_DGD=15|draw_DGD=7|loss_DGD=5|gf_DGD=44|ga_DGD=19\n|win_DGR=14|draw_DGR=6|loss_DGR=7|gf_DGR=44|ga_DGR=21\n|win_LIE=11|draw_LIE=7|loss_LIE=9|gf_LIE=54|ga_LIE=35\n|win_FCJ=7|draw_FCJ=5|loss_FCJ=15|gf_FC