rmo reizi v\u0113stur\u0113 p\u0101rdotas Latvijas virsl\u012bgas futbola \u010dempion\u0101ta interneta transl\u0101ciju ties\u012bbas &#124; Kasjauns.lv|publisher=kasjauns.lv|accessdate=December 1, 2015}}</ref> Since 2012, the league's homepage ''futbolavirsliga.lv'' has been active and since September 2012 this website has been accompanied by the InStat Football system, showing information and analysis of each match individually.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://futbolavirsliga.lv/index.php/jaunumi/780-virsliga-plano-ieviest-kvalitativu-statistikas-un-analizes-sistemu |title=Archived copy |access-date=2013-03-25 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130219030923/http://futbolavirsliga.lv/index.php/jaunumi/780-virsliga-plano-ieviest-kvalitativu-statistikas-un-analizes-sistemu |archive-date=2013-02-19 |url-status=dead }}</ref> Since October 2012, the Virsl\u012bga has also had its own analytical broadcast after each round of matches with football experts discussing the games and future events connected to Latvian football. It is transmitted via sportacentrs TV.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://futbolavirsliga.lv/index.php/jaunumi/1061-virsligai-savs-apskata-raidijums |title=Archived copy |access-date=2013-03-25 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130218233647/http://futbolavirsliga.lv/index.php/jaunumi/1061-virsligai-savs-apskata-raidijums |archive-date=2013-02-18 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n== League table ==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n\n|team1=VEN|name_VEN=[[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]]\n|team2=SKO|name_SKO=[[Skonto FC|Skonto]]\n|team3=DGD|name_DGD=[[FC Daugava|Daugava Daugavpils]]\n|team4=DGR|name_DGR=[[FK Daugava (2003)|Daugava R\u012bga]]\n|team5=LIE|name_LIE=[[FK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs|Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs]]\n|team6=FCJ|name_FCJ=[[FC J\u016brmala]]\n|team7=SPJ|name_SPJ=[[FK Spartaks J\u016brmala|Spartaks J\u016brmala]]\n|team8=JEL|name_JEL=[[FK Jelgava|Jelgava]]\n|team9=MLU|name_MLU=[[FS METTA/Latvijas Universit\u0101te|METTA/LU]]\n|team10=ILU