{"title_page": "H\u00e9ber Araujo dos Santos", "text_new": "{{short description|Brazilian footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2019}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = H\u00e9ber\n| image = \n| fullname = H\u00e9ber Araujo dos Santos\n| height = {{height|m=1.80}}\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1991|8|10}}\n| birth_place = [[Colorado do Oeste]], Brazil\n| currentclub = [[New York City FC|New York City]]\n| clubnumber = 9\n| position = [[Forward (association football)#Striker|Striker]]\n| youthyears1 = {{0|0000}}\u20132010\n| youthclubs1 = [[Figueirense FC|Figueirense]]\n| years1 = 2010\u20132011\n| clubs1 = [[Figueirense FC|Figueirense]]\n| caps1 = 28\n| goals1 = 6\n| years2 = 2011\u20132016\n| clubs2 = [[Coimbra Esporte Clube|Coimbra]]\n| caps2 = 0\n| goals2 = 0\n| years3 = 2013\n| clubs3 = \u2192 [[Clube Recreativo e Atl\u00e9tico Catalano|CRAC]] (loan)\n| caps3 = 13\n| goals3 = 7\n| years4 = 2014\n| clubs4 = \u2192 [[Ava\u00ed FC|Ava\u00ed]] (loan)\n| caps4 = 14\n| goals4 = 0\n| years5 = 2015\n| clubs5 = \u2192 [[Paysandu Sport Club|Paysandu]] (loan)\n| caps5 = \n| goals5 = \n| years6 = 2015\u20132016\n| clubs6 = \u2192 [[Alashkert FC|Alashkert]] (loan)\n| caps6 = 26\n| goals6 = 16\n| years7 = 2016\u20132017\n| clubs7 = [[NK Slaven Belupo|Slaven Belupo]]\n| caps7 = 30\n| goals7 = 10\n| years8 = 2017\u20132019\n| clubs8 = [[HNK Rijeka|Rijeka]]\n| caps8 = 38\n| goals8 = 25\n| years9 = 2019\u2013\n| clubs9 = [[New York City FC|New York City]]\n| caps9 = 22\n| goals9 = 15\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1 = \n| nationalcaps1 = \n| nationalgoals1 = \n| pcupdate = 11 October 2019\n| ntupdate = \n}}\n\n'''H\u00e9ber Araujo dos Santos''', known as '''H\u00e9ber''' (born 10 August 1991), is a Brazilian [[Association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Major League Soccer]] side [[New York City FC|New York City]] as a [[striker (association football)|striker]].\n\n==Club career==\nIn June 2016, H\u00e9ber joined [[HNK Rijeka|Rijeka]] from [[NK Slaven Belupo|Slaven Belupo]] for a transfer fee of \u20ac450,000.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://radio.hrt.hr/radio-rijeka/clanak/predstavljeni-puncec-i-heber-najavljeno-kekovo-potpisivanje-novog-ugovora/147832/ |title=Predstavljeni Pun\u010dec i Heber; najavljeno Kekovo potpisivanje novog ugovora |last=Vujnovi\u0107 |first=Korado |date=17 June 2017 |work=Radio Rijeka |language=Croatian |accessdate=18 June 2017}}</ref> He signed a three-year contract with the club with an option for a two-year extension.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nk-rijeka.hr/vijest/heber-arajuo-dos-santos-potpisao-za-rijeku-ovo-je-velika-cast-za-mene/ |title=Heber Arajuo dos Santos potpisao za Rijeku: Ovo je velika \u010dast za mene |date=17 June 2017 |work=HNK Rijeka |language=Croatian |accessdate=18 June 2017}}</ref>\n\nOn 21 March 2019, H\u00e9ber joined the [[Major League Soccer]] side [[New York City FC]].<ref>https://www.nycfc.com/post/2019/03/21/welcomeh-ber-h-ber-signs-new-york-city-fc</ref> He was the team\u2019s leading scorer for the 2019 season with 15 goals.\n\n==Club statistics ==\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:100%; text-align: center\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|[[2015\u201316 Armenian Premier League|2015\u201316]]\n|rowspan=\"1\" valign=\"center\"|[[Alashkert FC|Alashkert]]\n|rowspan=\"1\"|[[Armenian Premier League]]\n|26||16||4||3||4||1||34||20\n|-\n|[[2016\u201317 Croatian First Football League|2016\u201317]]\n|rowspan=\"1\" valign=\"center\"|[[NK Slaven Belupo|Slaven Belupo]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Croatian First Football League|Croatian First League]]\n|30||10||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||32||10\n|-\n|[[2017\u201318 HNK Rijeka season|2017\u201318]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" valign=\"center\"|[[HNK Rijeka|Rijeka]]\n|23||16||1||0||9||1||33||17\n|-\n|[[2018\u201319 HNK Rijeka season|2018\u